'''Imperial Customs Frigate 517''' was an [[Imperial Customs Frigate]] which once chased [[Hawker Bryce-Kelley]]'s [[Starship/Legends|starship]] ''[[Queen's Victory]]'' to the [[Reginard system/Legends|Reginard system]]. When they arrived in the [[Star system/Legends|system]], however, they were met with a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] ship and soon sent [[Customs Inspector]] [[Buudro]] to board the ship with two [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] guards. The Rebels managed to convince Buudro that they had not seen any ship enter the system, and so ''517'' left the system.<ref name="Death">{{ChallengeCite|76|Death by Triflexia}}</ref>

